{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775867225608,"sessionID":"ses_28611514fffeFkuK0ZyGHEguh4","part":{"id":"prt_d79ef6284001BBaWu06M52X7qz","messageID":"msg_d79ef357f001eUP52HkI1UIGo9","sessionID":"ses_28611514fffeFkuK0ZyGHEguh4","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-7d234b55f4294ce28e5538bb7ee78bc7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/doc.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/doc.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: // Package workloadmanager provides the HTTP service framework for the\n2: // WorkloadManager component of AgentCube. It includes HTTP server lifecycle\n3: // management, routing, middleware, health checking, and error handling.\n4: //\n5: // The package uses go-chi/chi for routing and follows Go standard library\n6: // conventions for HTTP handlers. Middleware chain executes in order:\n7: // Recovery → Logging → CORS → Handler.\n8: package workloadmanager\n\n(End of file - total 8 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"// Package workloadmanager provides the HTTP service framework for the\n// WorkloadManager component of AgentCube. It includes HTTP server lifecycle\n// management, routing, middleware, health checking, and error handling.\n//\n// The package uses go-chi/chi for routing and follows Go standard library\n// conventions for HTTP handlers. Middleware chain executes in order:\n// Recovery → Logging → CORS → Handler.\npackage workloadmanager","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/doc.go","time":{"start":1775867225593,"end":1775867225607}}}}
